---
description: UI and component conventions for src/components
globs:
  - "src/components/**"
alwaysApply: false
---

- Use Tailwind CSS for styling.
- Use Shadcn/UI (Radix primitives) for base components.
- Prefer Framer Motion for animations where needed.
- Organize components by domain (`post/`, `user/`, `communities/`, etc.).
- Leverage the custom background gradient system where applicable.


